  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 375 degrees Fahrenheit.",
    "Heat the olive oil in the terracotta dish over medium heat.",
    "Add the sliced almonds and cook until toasted, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Stir in the ground cumin and smoked paprika and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the dried dates, vegetable broth, salt, and black pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the dish with a lid and transfer to the preheated oven.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, then stir in the cooked brown rice.",
    "Return the dish to the oven and bake for an additional 10 minutes."
